        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3920143756" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16295214442034169045">The book is a much-needed historical romance that picks us up and sweeps our hearts and senses into the story, traveling abroad and back through generations, carrying us through the powerful emotions of war, love, heartbreak, and joy. I bear witness to Nicols&apos; efforts to be as true with detail as possible, knowing his painstaking period research, and his drawing on his own personal background in the story&apos;s locales. I highly recommend this book if you are involved in a book club, as he has a rea</span>
  <span id="freeText16295214442034169045" style="display:none">The book is a much-needed historical romance that picks us up and sweeps our hearts and senses into the story, traveling abroad and back through generations, carrying us through the powerful emotions of war, love, heartbreak, and joy. I bear witness to Nicols' efforts to be as true with detail as possible, knowing his painstaking period research, and his drawing on his own personal background in the story's locales. I highly recommend this book if you are involved in a book club, as he has a reader's guide available for those who wish to study the story in depth.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16295214442034169045" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
