<span id="freeTextContainer8336641507050053187">A World War II family generational epoch that spans decades and key elements of the story in London, throughout the U.K. and in America<br/><br/>This is the story of a man who lives his life according to the morals and values his parents instilled in him as a young man. It affects the lives of many others in positives ways, but unfortunately not his own nor a nurse who cared for him during the war. However, the end is fitting.<br/><br/>It&apos;s a love story with life lessons sprinkled throughout if the reader wants to </span>
  <span id="freeText8336641507050053187" style="display:none">A World War II family generational epoch that spans decades and key elements of the story in London, throughout the U.K. and in America<br /><br />This is the story of a man who lives his life according to the morals and values his parents instilled in him as a young man. It affects the lives of many others in positives ways, but unfortunately not his own nor a nurse who cared for him during the war. However, the end is fitting.<br /><br />It's a love story with life lessons sprinkled throughout if the reader wants to delve more deeply into a book that has several layers of the novel.<br /><br />I say to any reader between 15 and 95, read it!</span>
