        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3946644081" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7253568158764959473">Wow! I don’t usually enjoy novels set around war but I decided to give Alfred Nicol’s book a try after a friend recommended it to me. What an absolute gut punch! Of all the romance novels I’ve read this year, this has definitely been my favorite so far!! It’s rare to see a love triangle plot go so wrong and so, so right! Be ready to cry. If you’re anything like me, this book will move you to tears. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


